        "task": [
            "derive whole-stem growth rate from Lockhart-type turgor limitation applied at stem scale",
            "relate stem growth to whole-tree growth using stem allocation fraction u_S",
            "obtain closed-form growth expression under uniform osmotic potential and linear stem water-potential profile"
